Thank you.
How was your weekend?

13
00:01:44,167 --> 00:01:47,159
- Great. How was yours?
- Very nice. How are the kids?

14
00:01:47,327 --> 00:01:49,079
Great.

15
00:01:49,247 --> 00:01:52,045
<i>Magic trick. Henry!</i>

16
00:01:53,167 --> 00:01:54,600
- Jacob.
- Ted. Good Morning.

17
00:01:54,767 --> 00:01:56,439
- It's happening.
- What's happening?

18
00:01:56,607 --> 00:01:59,758
