approvals with Harry at 11.

23
00:02:15,007 --> 00:02:16,884
Close the door, please.

24
00:02:20,847 --> 00:02:23,042
How'd Henry's party go?

25
00:02:24,087 --> 00:02:26,203
- Terrific. He had a great time.
- Good.

26
