00:21:00,807 --> 00:21:03,560
Circle Foods. Take him, Mr. Cable.

308
00:21:04,567 --> 00:21:08,116
- We accept this juror, Your Honor.
- Mr. Rohr?

309
00:21:11,167 --> 00:21:13,522
- No objections, Your Honor.
- Thank you.

