356
00:23:04,127 --> 00:23:06,083
<i>You son of a bitch!</i>

357
00:23:06,247 --> 00:23:07,475
Help him.

358
00:23:07,967 --> 00:23:10,800
Help this man. Help this man.
Get him out of here.

359
00:23:12,407 --> 00:23:14,398
This is not a show in here.
Get him out.

360
00:23:14,567 --> 00:23:17,684
The nation's trying to kill itself.
You wanna give it the weapons.

361
00:23:18,487 --> 00:23:22,036
Son of a bitch! Let me go!
Let me go!

362
00:23:22,207 --> 00:23:24,801
Let me go! Bastards!

363
00:23:32,247 --> 00:23:34,078
Guess that's lunch.

364
00:23:35,527 --> 00:23:39,406
Somebody add "class clown" to
Mr. Easter's ever-expanding résumé.

365
00:23:39,807 --> 00:23:42,719
