366
00:23:42,887 --> 00:23:45,037
Attorneys, both of you,
in my chambers, now.

367
00:23:45,207 --> 00:23:46,686
<i>Good call.</i>

368
00:23:54,687 --> 00:23:57,679
<i>There are some things, however,</i>
<i>that seem to live eternal.</i>

369
00:23:57,847 --> 00:24:00,919
