423
00:26:58,127 --> 00:27:00,277
Hold on a minute there, Mr. Grimes.

424
00:27:00,447 --> 00:27:02,199
There's no need
for you to have come.

425
00:27:02,367 --> 00:27:04,085
You're excused for disability.

426
00:27:04,247 --> 00:27:06,238
What if I do not wish to be excused, sir?

427
00:27:06,407 --> 00:27:09,763
